Title: Back to Base
Description:
Getting this factory up and running will be a challenge, but I think we'll figure out something. Let's head back to Gundargaz and consult with a friend of ours.

His mind will be a big help to us here.
RewardText: Are you ready to put our heads together and come up with a plan?

Objectives.Text: Meet Brinthe at her home in Gundargaz
